What is the most basic memory app?

Step 1
-user creates questions with answers
  -keywords for categorization

Step 2
-user creates a course
  -add questions to the course
  -assign weights to the questions

Step 3
-user can chose a question list
  -presented with questions
    -questions are presented based on how recently it was answered, previous score, weight
  -answer the question
  -user scores their answer


